---
title: Open-Faced Turkey Patty Melts with Mushrooms, Gruyère, and Arugula Salad
description: We’re giving this diner favorite a healthy spin with lean ground turkey, sautéed mushrooms, and a healthy serving of greens. It’s still got all the juicy, cheesy greatness of the original, we promise! You can serve the patty melt open-faced or closed, depending on your preference!
